<p>I always enjoy knowing what people are reading. I ran across a handful of people, such as <a href="https://rknight.me/almanac/">Robb Knight</a>, <a href="https://bobmonsour.com/books/">Bob Monsour</a>, and <a href="https://thisguise.wtf/bookshelf/">Chazz Basuta</a>, with integrated bookshelves on their sites, and thought I would try it myself.</p>

<p>This page is powered by data from <a href="https://hardcover.app/">Hardcover</a> (my preferred book tracking app).</p>

<div class="container card-container">
  <div class="center-heading">
    <h2>Currently Reading</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    {%- for book in catalog.books.current %}
      {% include "bookitem.njk" %}
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>
  
  <hr/>

  <div class="center-heading">
    <h2>Favorite Books</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    {%- for book in catalog.books.favoriteBooks %}
      {% include "bookitem.njk" %}
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>

  <hr/>

  <div class="center-heading">
    <h2>All Books & Goals</h2>
  </div>

  <p>Please feel free to browse my entire reading catalog below. You can also jump to a specific year using the buttons below.</p>

  <div class="catalog-years">
    {% for year in catalog.books.years %}
      <div class="btn-nl-primary">
        <a href="#{{ year.year }}" class="tag-bubble">{{ year.year | replace("y", "") }}</a>{% if  not loop.last %} {% endif %}
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  {% set previous_year = "" %}
  {%- for book in catalog.books.datedBooks %}
    {%- set current_year = book.lastRead | truncate(4, true, '') -%}
    {%- if current_year != previous_year %}
      {% if not loop.first %}</div>{% endif %}
      <div class="center-heading catalog-year">
        <h4 id="y{{ current_year }}">{{ current_year }}</h4>
        {%- for goal in catalog.books.readingGoals %}
          {%- if goal.description == current_year %}
            <h5 class="center">Reading Goal: {{ goal.progress }} / {{ goal.goal }} books</h5>
          {%- endif %}
        {%- endfor %}
      </div>
      {% set previous_year = current_year %}
      <div class="row">
    {%- endif %}
    {% include "bookitem.njk" %}
  {%- endfor %}

  {%- if catalog.books.undatedBooks.length > 0 %}
    <div class="center-heading catalog-year">
      <h2 id="undated">Undated</h2>
      <span>Books that I've read that I don't have a completion date for.</span>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      {%- for book in catalog.books.undatedBooks %}
        {% include "bookitem.njk" %}
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  {%- endif %}
</div>